soloing, camping or anything else you wish to make an excuse about) and there shouldn't be a Verant mini-game to help you with those (as well as ignore the other players and possibly shirk your group responsibilities)...<P>"I think you have the rules wrong buddy, the game is for everyone, it is indeed made towards grouping but it is not for that only purpose at ALL times, because one also solos I don't thing that is against the rules. "<P>I never said that it was against the rules, I was pointing out that the last thing Verant needs to do is encourage people to do that (because there are enough anti-social people)...<P>"One can do many other things to negatively affect a group, gems is now just one of these options..."<P>Either way you missed the point, and Verant encouraging it is the point I'm making... The fact that "Gems" doesn't fit their neat little vision is what I'm saying here, and maybe along with learning how to add paragraphs you should work on reading comprehension... <BR>
