Gems is a Tetris-like game that is available in EQ.  Bring up your chat bar and type in /gems, and it takes you to the game.  Very simple little thing to pass the time while your warrior who foolishly solos too much sits and heals.    <IMG SRC="http://www.eqatlas.com/ubb/wink.gif"><P>----------------------<P>Kanammer<BR>Paladin of the Thirteenth Cycle<BR>Zebuxoruk<p>[This message has been edited by Kanammer (edited 07-12-2001).]
